quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Woe to every slanderous scandal-monger and backbiter
  104,2,Who collects wealth and counts it
  104,3,He thinks that his wealth can immortalize him
  104,4,Not so! He shall be hurled into El´Hutamah
  104,5,"Ah, what shall make you understand what El´Hutamah is"
  104,6,The Fire by Allah kindled
  104,7,Which leaps into the heart
  104,8,Lo! It closes in as a vault on them
  104,9,In outstretched columns